| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1501 — Recovery Inhibition (blacksuit)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 27d0bdcc-1ac4-57e2-84a3-05d547c4702e"
